reviewText: Pleased with the initial encounter: cute, friendly, thought-provoking from the first sight. Any chance to get this one with subtitles?

Jumbo is a little blue elephant who lives with his mother in a jungle. His father is never discussed, even though he wants to know who his dad was. Watch how he meets a little pink elephant, Sonia, gets trained by a Mahout to become a war elephant, and not only finds out about his father, but makes him proud by his deeds.
